## Development Workflow

### Working on Slides

```bash
# Start dev server (hot reload)
npm run dev

# Preview without watching
npm run preview

# Export to PowerPoint
npm run export

# Export to PDF
npm run export:pdf

# Build HTML
npm run build
```

### Best Practices

1. **Iterative Development**:
   - Run `npm run dev` while editing
   - Check content fits on each slide
   - Test all diagrams render correctly
   - Verify two-column layouts work

2. **Content Guidelines**:
   - One main idea per slide
   - Use visual hierarchy (headings, bullets)
   - Reference docs instead of showing code
   - Keep backup slides minimal

3. **Before Export**:
   - Review all slides for overflow
   - Check footer/pagination display
   - Verify diagrams render
   - Test in presentation mode

