- [ ] Content fits without overflow
- [ ] Two-column layouts render correctly
- [ ] Diagrams display properly
- [ ] Code references instead of full code
- [ ] Final slides (Questions/Thank You) are clean
- [ ] Backup slides are marked clearly

### Before Committing Documentation

- [ ] Proper markdown formatting
- [ ] Both ASCII and Mermaid diagrams where applicable
- [ ] Code examples are complete and working
- [ ] Cross-references are accurate
- [ ] Added to `/docs/README.md` index
- [ ] Use cases and best practices included
- [ ] External sources cited

## Troubleshooting

### Slides

**Content overflow**: Add scoped style to reduce font size
**Diagrams don't render**: Check `npm run dev` output for errors
**Footer missing**: Check `<!-- _footer: "" -->` not hiding it
**Two columns broken**: Verify scoped style is present

### Development

**Marp not found**: Run `npm install`
**Port in use**: Change port in `.marprc.yml`
**Hot reload not working**: Restart `npm run dev`

